#, sh-format
msgid "Oops. Supported driver not found"
msgstr "Ups. Controlador compatible no encontrado"

#: ../nvidia-detect-mx:440
#, sh-format
msgid "It is recommended to install the following:"
msgstr "Se recomienda instalar el siguiente:"

